      <span>func (*F) <a class="Documentation-source" href="https://cs.opensource.google/go/go/+/go1.26.2:src/testing/testing.go;l=1114">Output</a> <a class="Documentation-idLink" href="#F.Output" title="Go to F.Output" aria-label="Go to F.Output">¶</a></span>
  <span class="Documentation-sinceVersion">
    
