  </div><div class="Documentation-typeMethod">
    
  
  
    <h4 tabindex="-1" id="T.SkipNow" data-kind="method" class="Documentation-typeMethodHeader">
      <span>func (*T) <a class="Documentation-source" href="https://cs.opensource.google/go/go/+/go1.26.2:src/testing/testing.go;l=1253">SkipNow</a> <a class="Documentation-idLink" href="#T.SkipNow" title="Go to T.SkipNow" aria-label="Go to T.SkipNow">¶</a></span>
